# SP-2 Phase 13.1 — pretag verification evidence trail.
#
# lava-api-go/scripts/pretag-verify.sh writes <commit>.json files into this
# directory after a successful real-device user-flow run. scripts/tag.sh's
# api-go dispatch refuses to operate without a matching evidence file
# (Sixth Law clause 5: release tag gate).
#
# These JSON files ARE committed to git — the audit trail is durable per
# spec §15. Do NOT add `*.json` to .gitignore for this directory.
